    Event Timeline

    ae_plot.Rd

    Event Timeline

    ae_plot(data, footnote = "")

    Arguments

    data

    data.frame Adverse events data domain

    footnote

    character Footnote text

    Value

    htmlwidget Event timeline plotly object

    Examples

    data <- safetyCharts::stack_events() %>%
  dplyr::filter(
    !(is.na(.data$stdy) & is.na(.data$endy))
  ) %>%
  dplyr::arrange(
    .data$id, .data$stdy, .data$endy
  ) %>%
  dplyr::group_by(.data$id) %>%
  dplyr::mutate(
    seq = dplyr::row_number()
  ) %>%
  dplyr::ungroup()

data %>%
  dplyr::filter(
    .data$id == sample(unique(.data$id), 1)
  ) %>%
  ae_plot()
